kgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ch4X7sO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fch4X7sO.jpg&h=971c9013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests #Chinazi<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRepKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=b5806fd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour <br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.06"},{"pid":"8be9dd5223f7a42c991b89a6dfa087c1203e509c","tid":1559901,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c395d5643f6e6e41ee88cd1a88e6bb484e168eab","tid":1559901,"uid":49110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:31:09.000Z","msg":"休班警有棍，又無委任證...好難分...子彈都可以唔見，咁比人執到支棍咪可以亂打人？咁對拎住伸縮棍但又唔出示委任證嘅，會唔會係鄉黑？咁平民應該要立即衝上去將佢制服？伸縮棍係鄉黑打上，係可以打死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:38:54.000Z","msg":"影相拍片 之後一定要走"},{"pid":"deb7c465d659d8b18702d2b3d81bdea2b2fad9a5","tid":1559901,"uid":166947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:40:20.000Z","msg":"【保民聯】建制保皇 建設保民 香港值得更好的建設派<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560300\" data-auto-li